faqs.question: How do I start playing?
faqs.answer: Tap on a cow to begin a rhythm challenge and earn coins.

faqs.question: What do coins do?
faqs.answer: Coins let you purchase crops and upgrades from the shop.

faqs.question: How can I save my progress?
faqs.answer: Use the save option in the menu; the game also auto-saves periodically.
